==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outrider
<hw>Out"rid`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
summoner whose office is to cite men before the sheriff.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who rides out on horseback, beyond the main
group, e. g., as a scout.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A servant on horseback attending a
carriage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>outrigged</ent>⟦br⟧
